## Project Overview
clars.ai is a SaaS CRM built for freelancers and solopreneurs. It covers client management,
project tracking, invoicing, payment follow-up, and an AI assistant вЂ” all in one platform.
Target markets: Mena & Morocco (EN/AR/FR multilingual).

