### Backend
- **API Layer**: Next.js API Routes + tRPC
- **Auth**: NextAuth.js v5 (Google OAuth, Magic Link, Credentials)
- **Database**: MongoDB with Mongoose (ODM)
- **Cache**: Redis via Upstash
- **Job Queue**: BullMQ (reminders, auto-reminders, report generation)
- **Storage**: Cloudflare R2 (invoices, deliverables)

### AI & Integrations
- **LLM**: Gemini (assistant, email drafting, forecasting)
- **Payments**: Whop + Whop Billing
- **Email**: Resend (transactional + automated reminders)
- **Analytics**: PostHog

### Infrastructure
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions
- **Monitoring**: Sentry + Better Uptime

### Validation & Security
- **Validation**: Zod on all API routes
- **Tests**: Jest (unit) + Playwright (E2E) вЂ” target в‰Ґ 70% coverage
- **Linting**: ESLint + Prettier

