## Feature-Specific Rules

### Invoices
- Invoice number format: `INV-{YEAR}-{SEQUENCE}` e.g. `INV-2026-0042`
- Quote number format: `QUO-{YEAR}-{SEQUENCE}`
- Always store amounts in **cents** (integer) in DB; display formatted with currency
- Support: MAD, EUR, USD, GBP, SAR
- PDF template must include: logo, legal mentions, payment terms, QR code (optional)

### Client Health Score (AI)
- Score 0вЂ“100 computed async via BullMQ job on relevant events
- Factors: payment regularity, communication frequency, project volume, overdue invoices
- Stored in `Client.healthScore`, recalculated max once per day per client

### Multilingual (i18n)
- Use `next-intl` for translations
- Locales: `fr` (default), `en`, `ar`
- RTL layout activates automatically for `ar` locale
- All AI-generated content should match the user's selected language

### Auto-Reminders
- Sequences: J+7, J+14, J+30 after invoice due date
- Tone adapts to client profile (friendly в†’ firm в†’ formal)
- Never send reminders to clients marked as "disputed" without manual override
- Reminder emails use Resend with tracked opens

